Another reason why I should be on the council, people
listen to LNs ideas, while everyone hates me too much
to even bring up the subject (Winged Warrior maybe,
but Rudra wouldn't, and rAuq in the end seems to back
down quickly whenever he's in support of one of my
ideas at the start), so actually being on the council
is the only way I can ever get any of my ideas done. 
Besides LN doesn't rp anymore, he just makes comments,
and you all know he'd ban me.  Although I still
promise not to ban him for no reason.
